To better elucidate the enhancement of PEC performance after HsGDY encapsulated Cu2O NWs, incident photon-to-current-conversion efficiency (IPCE) measurements were conducted on Cu2O NWs and HsGDY@Cu2O NWs. The IPCE value was estimated and calculated with following equation:331IPCE(%)=1240I/λPlight×100%\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
